                    <p>
                        Web gateway supports the following channels:
                    </p>
                    <ol>
                        <li>
                            Web Sockets (bidirectional)
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            HTTP POST for sending
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            HTTP Long Polling for receiving
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                    <p>
                        Web gateway supports the following protocols:
                    </p>
                    <ol>
                        <li>
                            CoAP + Observe and No-Response options 
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            MQTT v3.1.1 
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            REST - though not really a protcol :-) 
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                    <p>
                        Web gateway supports the following content types :
                    </p>
                    <ol>
                        <li>
                            application/json
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            application/xml
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            text/plain
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            application/octet-stream
                        </li>
                    </ol>
